                &lt;span class=&quot;comment-copy&quot;&gt;It seems that &lt;code&gt;INHERITS&lt;/code&gt; pg functionality allows much more elegant querying, however the table/columns themselves are still set up exactly in concrete inheritance fashion: repeating all common attributes.  I don&apos;t think this removes any of the flaws already raised with concrete inheritance&lt;/span&gt;

